    public enum FTPFileOperationResult
extends java.lang.Enum<FTPFileOperationResult>
    Defines the possible outcomes for FTP file and directory operations. Each result corresponds to specific FTP response codes and indicates how the server should respond to file system commands like RETR, STOR, DELE, etc.

    This abstraction allows handler implementations to focus on file system logic without needing to know FTP protocol response codes.
